content: Disappointed! Why does it not keep track of my scores?
Whoever invented this game is a genius
No way to exit game without doing forced stop. Sent request for help, but did not receive a response back. Save your money and aggravation do not buy!
Love this game!

Not a bad game, but I liked it so much better when it kept scores properly. I used to be able to track my progress and beat my previous records, but in this version my scores and awards never change. Frustrating.
Awful since the update. Was my favorite game for years. Now it's close to unplayable. Not worth the time. Uninstalling from my phone.
I have played this for a few years, absolutely love it! But the past few days it exits the game in the middle of playing and goes to the scores, like you finished. Please fix
sadly the present version isn't user friendly at all... the navigation sucks, though the look and feel is similar to the earlier version
Used to be fun. Now constantly dumps game. Also dumps review. Terrible.
If it's not broken you shouldn't fix it. The original version was wonderful
I preferred the older version, the graphics on this version are to small and makes it hard to manipulate the letters.

The new interface is far inferior to the old version. I used to play all 
the time. I no longer want to play because I have to work too hard to 
switch letters.
Can I have the old version back and where are my high scores

My biggest complaint with this latest version is the reduced (sanitized) 
word list. The innocuos word 'sex' isn't recognized. Nor are any words on 
the blue list. I find this offensive. Don't restrict my vocabulary. All 
words should be allowed while players may choose which to use.
Great game, excellent brain challenge.
I play every day longest streak is 41 so far
A great way to relax a bit.  I wish there were increasing levels of difficulty.  Other than that I'm very pleased.

Dabble

This awesome, sweet game is my absolute favorite! It is challenging and just plain fun.
Great game that gives your brain a workout .....highly addictive
Really a fun and challenging word game !  Becomes even more fun as you play it more often.

Awesome
Love this game.  Never gets old. Great stress reliever...and stress inducer Lol! Great gameplay that never fails to entertain and challenge!
Couple of issues: doesn't always drag the letter you are aiming for, and the back button does not exit the app. Otherwise a great game.
Keeps me wicked smaht
At first it was difficult.  But the more you play, you'll see words faster. Then you want to break your highest scores.
Kind of hard
I absolutely love word games.  This one definitely challenges you!  I also love that it's not a mindless game.  Its an enjoyable way to keep your mind active and alert!
Otherwise absolutely love this game
I love word games. It was nice finding a fun and yet challenging game to play. Dabble is a great way to relax and unwind!
This game will grab you and never let you go. Absolutely LOVE it!!!!
This game makes you think and its addictive. I love a good challenge
Addictive fun.
great word game
Great game that keeps you thinking the whole time. We have the board game and this app is a great version to play on the go.
Just the best game ever! I am a "word app freak" and this is awesome.
Still come back to it years after installing

The app takes complete control of my audio. I can't control my music volume when I turned the sound down in the game.

Fun little game but needs some work to be a little more user friendly. Could easily be a 4 to 5 start game with a couple of minor tweaks.  Needs an unobtrusive notification system for when invites are received and new games are ready.  Needs a way to easily compare scores. It's difficult to see and compare the scores of sent games. Have a setting that shows all pay games, your score and time and that of your opponent. Similar to the way it's displayed on the Facebook app. Overall stats would be great too.
BEWARE:  HIGHLY ADDICTIVE!!!
Fun game. Definitely more than 2 bucks worth of amusement.
I have this game on my nook. It is extremely addicting!
Fun and addicting. I play this game a lot.
I have this game on every divice we own. My only problem is there is no exit. I have to home page, task manager then exit. Would like to exit my game without it still running.
Even if It does not work perfectly on my phone samsung III  My biggest complain is thst i cant find it on my kinfle fire 8.9 ; please do something !
Good word game.  Makes you think.
I only meant to play for a few minutes before going to bed, and dang it, it's now 3am and I have to be up in 5 hours... Great Game!
As has been mentioned by others, longest streaks should show the longest independent streaks.
Love this game, when I can play it.

I love the board game and the Dabble app is almost as good. If you could create a pause play button for life's interruptions I'd play more often throughout the day. PLUS please make it where the game doesn't automatically solve when time runs out. I want to figure it out. That's half the fun!!!!! You make those two options available  and you deserve 5 STARS!!!! Great game!
This app needs to keep the longest streak record separate for each streak.  If I get a win streak of 50 games, then it should not also register 49 and 48 and 47, etc...
Addictive thorough enjoyable love the music
Quick thinking fun game. Would recommend to anyone.
Love this game!! Keeps me entertained for hours! :D
I absolutely love this game. I am totally addicted. I give it 5 stars when you configure it to connect with Facebook OR make it do you can play with random people.

Fun word game.  I would like to see other possible answers after I have entered mine so I could learn how to get better scores!  I also would like it better if when I got the puzzle complete it didn't automatically submit my answers.  Sometimes I am trying different things to get a higher score and I accidentally make words to complete the puzzle.  I would prefer to submit my answers when I think that I have a good score.
Facebook don't work please fix in next update
Love this game, play it all the time, never gets old
Won't connect to facebook, so I can't challenge friends. :(  Otherwise,  great game!
Great game! Wish there was a way to  see the maximum score possible and the solution for each puzzle. Maybe in the next update?
5 stars when I can outside pause the game n not totally sit quit out
Overall, this is a very enjoyable game, but the dictionary is not a comprehensive as I would like, which makes it a bit frustrating at times, especially if you are a keen scrabble player.
If you like thinking games it gets boring quick
Works well for the Nexus 7 ..Didn't think it would being that I saw reviehw that didn't work for ICS phones
2 issues: -Limited dictionary -back button should return to the previous page, not close the app
Fun game ruined because half (yes half) of the 2 letter words in the dictionary don't work here. Scrabble fans will curse this game forever until they fix it.
Not supported, some major flaws like dictionary, doesn't handle accidental closes or incoming calls, kills your win streak if that happens. Could be good if they supported it more than two seconds
Just enjoy the time away from everyday concerns with this game.
Very addicting!
Fun! Good idea for a word game.
BUT flawed dictionary. I cant believe i have to work around its ignorance just so i can finish a game. Wont accept words like ID, RE etc.
If you enjoy word games this is perfect.
Love the game, tile sounds, time limit - not too short, and CHALLENGE!!!!

I wanted to love this game but I've played about 20 games now and there were at least a dozen standard words that the game did not know.  This is especially annoying with the "2 letter word" category.  Not sure how legit all of this 5 star reviews are.  There is a good game here with some dictionary updates.
Finally!  a fun, addictive, single-player word game
Thanks for producing this great game.  Very entertaining and challenging.
Watched my snoopy play the game and i was enthralled.
Holy crap this game is addictive. Must. Stop. Now.
Very well done, great game!

Lots of fun!
Hard but very well done.  Keeps you going.
Not a whole lot of variety but a fairly good game. Well worth it.

Super fun!

Fantastic! I decided to tryout a new game, and this game was definitley worth it, its very competitive and addictive! Great buy.
